ats don't cleanly map to them either.\n\nTo actually compare their lead styles, I'd need one of:\n1. **Separate solo runs** — nights where each commands alone — so I can compare K/D, win rate, fight tempo, and squad deaths per fight between them. If you tell me they tag on different nights, I can pull each one's history.\n2. **Precise replay enabled** in AxiBridge's recorder settings for future runs, which would let me compare tag paths, engage distance, and how tight each keeps the squad.\n\nWant me to look across the broader run history to see if Baba and DRAFT each have solo nights I can contrast?","filedAt":"12:21 PM","tools":[{"name":"axibridge_commander_stats","display":{"kind":"table","data":{"title":"Commanders","columns":[{"key":"account","label":"Commander"},{"key":"fightsLed","label":"Fights led"},{"key":"wins","label":"W"},{"key":"losses","label":"L"},{"key":"kdr","label":"KDR"},{"key":"deaths","label":"Deaths"}],"rows":[{"account":"Qweqweqwe.8356","profession":"Holosmith","runs":14,"fightsLed":156,"wins":109,"losses":47,"kdr":1.76,"kills":1304,"deaths":44},{"account":"maestro.9016","profession":"Firebrand","runs":6,"fightsLed":98,"wins":86,"losses":12,"kdr":3.9,"kills":1479,"deaths":7},{"account":"Xenoma.6087","profession":"Mirage","runs":5,"fightsLed":32,"wins":25,"losses":7,"kdr":3.28,"kills":272,"deaths":4},{"account":"Ali.2903","profession":"Tempest","runs":3,"fightsLed":69,"wins":56,"losses":13,"kdr":3.73,"kills":1228,"deaths":4},{"account":"chromatic.2649","profession":"Tempest","runs":2,"fightsLed":28,"wins":15,"losses":13,"kdr":0.89,"kills":108,"deaths":11},{"account":"Moun.9740","profession":"Spellbreaker","runs":1,"fightsLed":5,"wins":5,"losses":0,"kdr":17.33,"kills":52,"deaths":0},{"account":"Cortiz.8203","profession":"Druid","runs":1,"fightsLed":1,"wins":1,"losses":0,"kdr":6,"kills":6,"deaths":0},{"account":"darks luke.6524","profession":"Firebrand","runs":3,"fightsLed":34,"wins":23,"losses":11,"kdr":1.1,"kills":640,"deaths":18},{"account":"